properties.name: Path
properties.expression: function limbPath() {        // Limber Path Limb        const thisProp = thisProperty;        const endctrl = thisComp.layer('{{ end }}');        const curveLin = endctrl('ADBE Effect Parade')('Pseudo/skl_main_data_01')('curvature').value[1] * 0.01;        if (curveLin === 0) {            return createPath([                endctrl('ADBE Effect Parade')('Pseudo/skl_main_data_01')('p0').value,                endctrl('ADBE Effect Parade')('Pseudo/skl_main_data_01')('p1ikfkfreek').value,                endctrl('ADBE Effect Parade')('Pseudo/skl_main_data_01')('p2ikfkfreek').value,            ], [], [], false);        }        else {            const inTangPos = endctrl('ADBE Effect Parade')('Pseudo/skl_main_data_01')('inTangPos').value;            const outTangPos = endctrl('ADBE Effect Parade')('Pseudo/skl_main_data_01')('outTangPos').value;            return createPath([                endctrl('ADBE Effect Parade')('Pseudo/skl_main_data_01')('p0').value,                endctrl('ADBE Effect Parade')('Pseudo/skl_main_data_01')('p1ikfkfreek').value,                endctrl('ADBE Effect Parade')('Pseudo/skl_main_data_01')('p2ikfkfreek').value,            ], [[0, 0], inTangPos, [0, 0]], [[0, 0], mul(outTangPos, -1), [0, 0]], false);        }    }limbPath();// Limber Library limbPath

properties.name: Scale
Scale
properties.expression: let val = [100, 100]if (thisLayer.hasParent) {    const ctrlScaleFactor = Math.max(thisLayer.length(thisLayer.toComp([0, 0]), thisLayer.toComp([0.7071, 0.7071])), 0.0001);    val = [value[0] / ctrlScaleFactor, value[1] / ctrlScaleFactor]}val
